    "parse": {
      "title": "Warp Totem",
      "pageid": 2872,
      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Warp Totems</b> are items that can be used as instant transport to different areas on the map. They can be <a href=\"/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\">crafted</a>, earned, or purchased at the <a href=\"/Casino\" title=\"Casino\">Casino</a>, and are used to quickly travel to different parts of the Valley. Crafting recipes come from leveling up <a href=\"/Foraging\" title=\"Foraging\">Foraging</a> skill or purchasing at various vendors. To use a Warp Totem, select it in inventory and \"use\" it (right-click).\n</p><p>Later in the game there are permanent teleporters available which replace consumable Warp Totems. They function much the same way, but are not consumed on use.\n</p><p>There are five locations that standard Warp Totems will teleport players to:  <a href=\"/The_Farm\" title=\"The Farm\">The Farm</a>, <a href=\"/The_Mountain\" title=\"The Mountain\">The Mountain</a>, <a href=\"/The_Beach\" title=\"The Beach\">The Beach</a>, <a href=\"/The_Desert\" title=\"The Desert\">The Desert</a>, and <a href=\"/Ginger_Island\" title=\"Ginger Island\">Ginger Island</a>.\n</p><p>Note that on the day of the <a href=\"/Luau\" title=\"Luau\">Luau</a> and <a href=\"/Dance_of_the_Moonlight_Jellies\" title=\"Dance of the Moonlight Jellies\">Dance of the Moonlight Jellies</a>, the <a href=\"/Warp_Totem:_Beach\" title=\"Warp Totem: Beach\">Warp Totem: Beach</a> will be consumed upon use, but will not transport the player to <a href=\"/The_Beach\" title=\"The Beach\">the Beach</a> outside of festival time. During festival time, the totem will be consumed, and will transport the player to the festival, as if they had entered the beach via the bridge from <a href=\"/Pelican_Town\" title=\"Pelican Town\">Pelican Town</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Farm\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Farm</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Mountains\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Mountains</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Beach\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Beach</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Desert\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Desert</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Ginger_Island\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Ginger Island</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Farm\">Farm</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Warp_Totem&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Farm\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"padding-bottom: 8px;\"><img alt=\"Warp Totem Farm.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Warp_Totem_Farm.png/24px-Warp_Totem_Farm.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Warp_Totem_Farm.png/36px-Warp_Totem_Farm.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/e4/Warp_Totem_Farm.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Warp_Totem:_Farm\" title=\"Warp Totem: Farm\">Warp Totem: Farm</a> warps you directly to <a href=\"/The_Farm\" title=\"The Farm\">the farm warp statue</a>. It is consumed on use.</li>\n<li><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Return Scepter.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f3/Return_Scepter.png/24px-Return_Scepter.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f3/Return_Scepter.png/36px-Return_Scepter.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f3/Return_Scepter.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Return_Scepter\" title=\"Return Scepter\">Return Scepter</a></span> warps you directly to <a href=\"/The_Farm\" title=\"The Farm\">the farm house</a>. For farmhands in a multiplayer game, it warps you directly to <a href=\"/Cabin\" title=\"Cabin\">your cabin</a>. It is not consumed on use.</li>\n<li><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Farm Obelisk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/34/Farm_Obelisk.png/24px-Farm_Obelisk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"64\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/34/Farm_Obelisk.png/36px-Farm_Obelisk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/3/34/Farm_Obelisk.png/48px-Farm_Obelisk.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Farm_Obelisk\" title=\"Farm Obelisk\">Farm Obelisk</a></span> warps you directly to <a href=\"/The_Farm\" title=\"The Farm\">the farm warp statue</a>. It's an unlockable building on the <a href=\"/Ginger_Island\" title=\"Ginger Island\">Ginger Island</a> farm, and is not consumed on use.</li>\n<li><img alt=\"Mini-Obelisk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c9/Mini-Obelisk.png/24px-Mini-Obelisk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c9/Mini-Obelisk.png/36px-Mini-Obelisk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/c9/Mini-Obelisk.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Mini-Obelisk\" title=\"Mini-Obelisk\">Mini-Obelisks</a> transport you between two places on the Farm.  They are not consumed on use.</li>\n</ul>\n<table>\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120947\">.mw-parser-output .mapcontainer{position:relative;overflow:hidden}.mw-parser-output .maplocation{position:absolute}</style><div class=\"mapcontainer\" style=\"width:400px;height:244px;\"><div class=\"maplocation\" style=\"left:140px;top:75px;\"><img alt=\"Maplocation.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5c/Maplocation.png/20px-Maplocation.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5c/Maplocation.png/30px-Maplocation.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5c/Maplocation.png/40px-Maplocation.png 2x\" /></div><img alt=\"Map.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/4/43/Map.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"244\" /></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Warp_Totem_Farm_location.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Warp Totem Farm location.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/2f/Warp_Totem_Farm_location.png/428px-Warp_Totem_Farm_location.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"428\" height=\"244\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/2f/Warp_Totem_Farm_location.png/642px-Warp_Totem_Farm_location.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/2/2f/Warp_Totem_Farm_location.png/855px-Warp_Totem_Farm_location.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Mountains\">Mountains</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Warp_Totem&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Mountains\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"padding-bottom: 8px;\"><img alt=\"Warp Totem Mountains.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d8/Warp_Totem_Mountains.png/24px-Warp_Totem_Mountains.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d8/Warp_Totem_Mountains.png/36px-Warp_Totem_Mountains.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/d8/Warp_Totem_Mountains.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Warp_Totem:_Mountains\" title=\"Warp Totem: Mountains\">Warp Totem: Mountains</a> warps you directly to <a href=\"/The_Mountain\" title=\"The Mountain\">The Mountain</a>. It is consumed on use.</li>\n<li><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Earth Obelisk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/3c/Earth_Obelisk.png/24px-Earth_Obelisk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"64\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/3c/Earth_Obelisk.png/36px-Earth_Obelisk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/3/3c/Earth_Obelisk.png/48px-Earth_Obelisk.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Earth_Obelisk\" title=\"Earth Obelisk\">Earth Obelisk</a></span> warps you directly to <a href=\"/The_Mountain\" title=\"The Mountain\">The Mountain</a>. It's a placeable building on the farm, and is not consumed on use.</li>\n</ul>\n<table>\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120947\"/><div class=\"mapcontainer\" style=\"width:400px;height:244px;\"><div class=\"maplocation\" style=\"left:255px;top:40px;\"><img alt=\"Maplocation.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5c/Maplocation.png/20px-Maplocation.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5c/Maplocation.png/30px-Maplocation.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5c/Maplocation.png/40px-Maplocation.png 2x\" /></div><img alt=\"Map.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/4/43/Map.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"244\" /></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Warp_Totem_Mountain_location.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Warp Totem Mountain location.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d8/Warp_Totem_Mountain_location.png/427px-Warp_Totem_Mountain_location.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"427\" height=\"244\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d8/Warp_Totem_Mountain_location.png/641px-Warp_Totem_Mountain_location.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/d8/Warp_Totem_Mountain_location.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Beach\">Beach</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Warp_Totem&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Beach\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"padding-bottom: 8px;\"><img alt=\"Warp Totem Beach.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/2f/Warp_Totem_Beach.png/24px-Warp_Totem_Beach.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/2f/Warp_Totem_Beach.png/36px-Warp_Totem_Beach.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/2/2f/Warp_Totem_Beach.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Warp_Totem:_Beach\" title=\"Warp Totem: Beach\">Warp Totem: Beach</a> warps you directly to <a href=\"/The_Beach\" title=\"The Beach\">The Beach</a>. It is consumed on use.</li>\n<li><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Water Obelisk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/b7/Water_Obelisk.png/24px-Water_Obelisk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"64\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/b7/Water_Obelisk.png/36px-Water_Obelisk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/b/b7/Water_Obelisk.png/48px-Water_Obelisk.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Water_Obelisk\" title=\"Water Obelisk\">Water Obelisk</a></span> warps you directly to the <a href=\"/The_Beach\" title=\"The Beach\">The Beach</a>. It's a placeable building on the farm, and is not consumed on use.</li>\n</ul>\n<table>\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120947\"/><div class=\"mapcontainer\" style=\"width:400px;height:244px;\"><div class=\"maplocation\" style=\"left:247px;top:170px;\"><img alt=\"Maplocation.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5c/Maplocation.png/20px-Maplocation.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5c/Maplocation.png/30px-Maplocation.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5c/Maplocation.png/40px-Maplocation.png 2x\" /></div><img alt=\"Map.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/4/43/Map.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"244\" /></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Warp_Totem_Beach_location.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Warp Totem Beach location.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/96/Warp_Totem_Beach_location.png/427px-Warp_Totem_Beach_location.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"427\" height=\"244\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/96/Warp_Totem_Beach_location.png/641px-Warp_Totem_Beach_location.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/96/Warp_Totem_Beach_location.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Desert\">Desert</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Warp_Totem&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Desert\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"padding-bottom: 8px;\"><img alt=\"Warp Totem Desert.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/83/Warp_Totem_Desert.png/24px-Warp_Totem_Desert.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/83/Warp_Totem_Desert.png/36px-Warp_Totem_Desert.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/83/Warp_Totem_Desert.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Warp_Totem:_Desert\" title=\"Warp Totem: Desert\">Warp Totem: Desert</a> warps you directly to <a href=\"/The_Desert\" title=\"The Desert\">The Desert</a>. It is consumed on use.</li>\n<li><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Desert Obelisk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/60/Desert_Obelisk.png/24px-Desert_Obelisk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"64\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/60/Desert_Obelisk.png/36px-Desert_Obelisk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/6/60/Desert_Obelisk.png/48px-Desert_Obelisk.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Desert_Obelisk\" title=\"Desert Obelisk\">Desert Obelisk</a></span> warps you directly to the <a href=\"/The_Desert\" title=\"The Desert\">The Desert</a>. It's a placeable building on the farm, and is not consumed on use.</li>\n</ul>\n<table>\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120947\"/><div class=\"mapcontainer\" style=\"width:400px;height:244px;\"><div class=\"maplocation\" style=\"left:30px;top:20px;\"><img alt=\"Maplocation.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5c/Maplocation.png/20px-Maplocation.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5c/Maplocation.png/30px-Maplocation.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5c/Maplocation.png/40px-Maplocation.png 2x\" /></div><img alt=\"Map.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/4/43/Map.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"244\" /></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Warp_Totem_Desert_location.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Warp Totem Desert location.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f6/Warp_Totem_Desert_location.png/427px-Warp_Totem_Desert_location.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"427\" height=\"244\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f6/Warp_Totem_Desert_location.png/641px-Warp_Totem_Desert_location.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f6/Warp_Totem_Desert_location.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Ginger_Island\">Ginger Island</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Warp_Totem&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Ginger Island\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"padding-bottom: 8px;\"><img alt=\"Warp Totem Island.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/b9/Warp_Totem_Island.png/24px-Warp_Totem_Island.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/b9/Warp_Totem_Island.png/36px-Warp_Totem_Island.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/b/b9/Warp_Totem_Island.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Warp_Totem:_Island\" title=\"Warp Totem: Island\">Warp Totem: Island</a> warps you directly to <a href=\"/Ginger_Island\" title=\"Ginger Island\">Ginger Island</a>. It is consumed on use.</li>\n<li><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Island Obelisk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/18/Island_Obelisk.png/24px-Island_Obelisk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"64\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/18/Island_Obelisk.png/36px-Island_Obelisk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/18/Island_Obelisk.png/48px-Island_Obelisk.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Island_Obelisk\" title=\"Island Obelisk\">Island Obelisk</a></span> warps you directly to the <a href=\"/Ginger_Island\" title=\"Ginger Island\">Ginger Island</a>. It's a placeable building on the farm, and is not consumed on use.</li>\n</ul>\n<table>\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120947\"/><div class=\"mapcontainer\" style=\"width:400px;height:244px;\"><div class=\"maplocation\" style=\"left:195px;top:135px;\"><img alt=\"Maplocation.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5c/Maplocation.png/20px-Maplocation.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5c/Maplocation.png/30px-Maplocation.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5c/Maplocation.png/40px-Maplocation.png 2x\" /></div><img alt=\"Ginger Island Map.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/4/47/Ginger_Island_Map.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"244\" /></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Warp_Totem_Island_location.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Warp Totem Island location.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d3/Warp_Totem_Island_location.png/434px-Warp_Totem_Island_location.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"434\" height=\"244\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d3/Warp_Totem_Island_location.png 1.5x\" /></a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Warp_Totem&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.0\" title=\"Version History\">1.0</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.1\" title=\"Version History\">1.1</a>: Added permanent teleporters (<a href=\"/Return_Scepter\" title=\"Return Scepter\">Return Scepter</a>, <a href=\"/Earth_Obelisk\" title=\"Earth Obelisk\">Earth Obelisk</a>, <a href=\"/Water_Obelisk\" title=\"Water Obelisk\">Water Obelisk</a>).</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Added desert teleporters (<a href=\"/Warp_Totem:_Desert\" title=\"Warp Totem: Desert\">Warp Totem: Desert</a>, <a href=\"/Desert_Obelisk\" title=\"Desert Obelisk\">Desert Obelisk</a>).</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5\" title=\"Version History\">1.5</a>: Added island teleporters (<a href=\"/Warp_Totem:_Island\" title=\"Warp Totem: Island\">Warp Totem: Island</a>, <a href=\"/Island_Obelisk\" title=\"Island Obelisk\">Island Obelisk</a>).  Added <a href=\"/Mini-Obelisk\" title=\"Mini-Obelisk\">Mini-Obelisk</a>.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Totems\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Warp Totems</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Warp_Totem:_Beach\" title=\"Warp Totem: Beach\">Warp Totem: Beach</a> • <a href=\"/Warp_Totem:_Desert\" title=\"Warp Totem: Desert\">Warp Totem: Desert</a> • <a href=\"/Warp_Totem:_Farm\" title=\"Warp Totem: Farm\">Warp Totem: Farm</a> • <a href=\"/Warp_Totem:_Island\" title=\"Warp Totem: Island\">Warp Totem: Island</a> • <a href=\"/Warp_Totem:_Mountains\" title=\"Warp Totem: Mountains\">Warp Totem: Mountains</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Permanent Teleporters</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Desert_Obelisk\" title=\"Desert Obelisk\">Desert Obelisk</a> • <a href=\"/Earth_Obelisk\" title=\"Earth Obelisk\">Earth Obelisk</a> • <a href=\"/Farm_Obelisk\" title=\"Farm Obelisk\">Farm Obelisk</a> • <a href=\"/Island_Obelisk\" title=\"Island Obelisk\">Island Obelisk</a> • <a href=\"/Return_Scepter\" title=\"Return Scepter\">Return Scepter</a> • <a href=\"/Water_Obelisk\" title=\"Water Obelisk\">Water Obelisk</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Other Totems\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Mini-Obelisk\" title=\"Mini-Obelisk\">Mini-Obelisk</a> • <a href=\"/Rain_Totem\" title=\"Rain Totem\">Rain Totem</a> • <a href=\"/Treasure_Totem\" title=\"Treasure Totem\">Treasure Totem</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260413225824\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.064 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.077 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1511/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5626/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 695/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3341/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   26.326      1 -total\n 55.40%   14.586      6 Template:Name\n 21.96%    5.781      5 Template:Map\n 13.32%    3.506      4 Template:History\n  8.28%    2.180      4 Template:Version\n  6.20%    1.633      1 Template:NavboxWarpTotems\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:2872-0!canonical and timestamp 20260413225824 and revision id 187109\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "\n'''Warp Totems''' are items that can be used as instant transport to different areas on the map. They can be [[Crafting|crafted]], earned, or purchased at the [[Casino]], and are used to quickly travel to different parts of the Valley. Crafting recipes come from leveling up [[Foraging]] skill or purchasing at various vendors. To use a Warp Totem, select it in inventory and \"use\" it (right-click).\n\nLater in the game there are permanent teleporters available which replace consumable Warp Totems. They function much the same way, but are not consumed on use.\n\nThere are five locations that standard Warp Totems will teleport players to:  [[The Farm]], [[The Mountain]], [[The Beach]], [[The Desert]], and [[Ginger Island]].\n\nNote that on the day of the [[Luau]] and [[Dance of the Moonlight Jellies]], the [[Warp Totem: Beach]] will be consumed upon use, but will not transport the player to [[the Beach]] outside of festival time. During festival time, the totem will be consumed, and will transport the player to the festival, as if they had entered the beach via the bridge from [[Pelican Town]].\n\n==Farm==\n<ul>\n<li style=\"padding-bottom: 8px;\">[[File:Warp Totem Farm.png|24px|link=]] [[Warp Totem: Farm]] warps you directly to [[The Farm|the farm warp statue]]. It is consumed on use.</li>\n<li>{{name|Return Scepter|class=inline}} warps you directly to [[The Farm|the farm house]]. For farmhands in a multiplayer game, it warps you directly to [[Cabin|your cabin]]. It is not consumed on use.</li>\n<li>{{name|Farm Obelisk|class=inline}} warps you directly to [[The Farm|the farm warp statue]]. It's an unlockable building on the [[Ginger Island]] farm, and is not consumed on use.</li>\n<li>[[File:Mini-Obelisk.png|24px|link=]] [[Mini-Obelisk]]s transport you between two places on the Farm.  They are not consumed on use.</li>\n</ul>\n{|\n|-\n|{{Map|140|75}}\n|[[File:Warp Totem Farm location.png|x244px]]\n|}\n\n==Mountains==\n<ul>\n<li style=\"padding-bottom: 8px;\">[[File: Warp Totem Mountains.png|24px|link=]] [[Warp Totem: Mountains]] warps you directly to [[The Mountain]]. It is consumed on use.</li>\n<li>{{name|Earth Obelisk|class=inline}} warps you directly to [[The Mountain]]. It's a placeable building on the farm, and is not consumed on use.</li>\n</ul>\n{|\n|-\n|{{Map|255|40}}\n|[[File:Warp Totem Mountain location.png|x244px]]\n|}\n\n==Beach==\n<ul>\n<li style=\"padding-bottom: 8px;\">[[File:Warp Totem Beach.png|24px|link=]] [[Warp Totem: Beach]] warps you directly to [[The Beach]]. It is consumed on use.</li>\n<li>{{name|Water Obelisk|class=inline}} warps you directly to the [[The Beach]]. It's a placeable building on the farm, and is not consumed on use.</li>\n</ul>\n{|\n|-\n|{{Map|247|170}}\n|[[File:Warp Totem Beach location.png|x244px]]\n|}\n\n==Desert==\n<ul>\n<li style=\"padding-bottom: 8px;\">[[File:Warp Totem Desert.png|24px|link=]] [[Warp Totem: Desert]] warps you directly to [[The Desert]]. It is consumed on use.</li>\n<li>{{name|Desert Obelisk|class=inline}} warps you directly to the [[The Desert]]. It's a placeable building on the farm, and is not consumed on use.</li>\n</ul>\n{|\n|-\n|{{Map|30|20}}\n|[[File:Warp Totem Desert location.png|x244px]]\n|}\n\n==Ginger Island==\n<ul>\n<li style=\"padding-bottom: 8px;\">[[File:Warp Totem Island.png|24px|link=]] [[Warp Totem: Island]] warps you directly to [[Ginger Island]]. It is consumed on use.</li>\n<li>{{name|Island Obelisk|class=inline}} warps you directly to the [[Ginger Island]]. It's a placeable building on the farm, and is not consumed on use.</li>\n</ul>\n{|\n|-\n|{{Map|main=false|island=true|islandloc1x=195|islandloc1y=135}}\n|[[File:Warp Totem Island location.png|x244px]]\n|}\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.0|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.1|Added permanent teleporters ([[Return Scepter]], [[Earth Obelisk]], [[Water Obelisk]]). }}\n{{History|1.4|Added desert teleporters ([[Warp Totem: Desert]], [[Desert Obelisk]]). }}\n{{History|1.5|Added island teleporters ([[Warp Totem: Island]], [[Island Obelisk]]).  Added [[Mini-Obelisk]]. }}\n\n{{NavboxWarpTotems}}\n\n[[Category:Warp Totems]]\n[[Category:Method of travel]]\n\n[[de:Teleport-Totem]]\n[[es:Tótem de viaje]]\n[[fr:Totem de téléportation]]\n[[it:Teletra-Totem]]\n[[ja:ワープトーテム]]\n[[ko:워프 토템]]\n[[hu:Teleport totem]]\n[[pt:Totem de teletransporte]]\n[[ru:Тотем-телепорт]]\n[[tr:Işınlanma Totemi]]\n[[zh:传送图腾]]"
